  <participating-org role="4" type="90">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Wake It Up Technology Joint Stock L</narrative>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Wake It Up is an online and offline platform for community to create, manage and participate easily in social activities and campaigns. Its slogan is Connect People, Collect Power. Wake It Up#s mission is to help gather social#s power to solve social#s issues. Byvariety of interactions, Wake It Up creates space and rooms for entrepreneurs, different organizations and communities to co # operate and translate their ideas into real actions to solve social issues related to inequality, poverty and open environment for start# up. With Wake It Up, campaign and social event conduction become much easier and more efficient than ever before.

Apart from offline public relationship building, our website Wakeitup.net can be regarded as one of most powerful platform for online campaigning.It has three main functions including petition, share funding and competition. With Wakeitup.net people can collect signatures of the community to support certain ideas or to make a proposed solution to be accepted by the government. They also can do fundraising and participate in various competitions for example a competition call for solutions addressing education gap among different groups. One of  the most successful campaign recently is #Justice for Toan# which is a signature collecting campaign to request the Ministry of Health to find out the cause of unreasonable death of a flight attendant. The campaign attracts 10,000 supporting signatures of community and involvement of media which urges the Ministry of Health to take action after two days.

Wake It Up was founded by Mr. Hoang Duc Minh, a young social activist. Mr. Minh was awarded as a promising young leader in 30Under30 by Forbes in 2015</narrative>
